A funeral service was held for the Lagos-based lawyer, Bolanle Raheem, who was shot dead in the Ajah area of the state on Christmas Day. Suspended Assistant Superintendent of Police (ASP), Drambi Vandi, gunned down the pregnant lawyer in the presence of her family members. On Tuesday, the Redeemed Christian Church of God (RCCG), Olive Branch, Banana Island, Ikoyi, Lagos, held a funeral service for her. Below are pictures and videos: 